.QUIT
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |  QUIT                                                                |
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 
 Exits from Rim.
 
*
.REFORMAT
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |  REFORMAT column TO format <IN table>                                |
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 
 Changes the format of the specified column.  If no table name
