=fmt
 
*
.RENAME COLUMN
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |  RENAME <COLUMN> column TO new_name <IN table>                       |
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 
 Changes the name of the specified column to 'new_name'.  If no
