*
.RENAME LINK
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |  RENAME LINK link TO new_name                                        |
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 
 Changes the name of the specified link to 'new_name'.
 
*
.RENAME TABLE
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |  RENAME TABLE table TO new_name                                      |
